"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"@Balajis - former CTO at Coinbase and a16z partner recently published an article about why crypto should be included in the Indiastack\\n\\nBefore we take a closer look at the bull case for including crypto …\\n\\n… let’s understand Indiastack\\n\\nIndiastack is set of national APIs for payments, identity, KYC, e-signature, and document verification that scales to a billion people\\n\\nWhile other countries have implemented similar solutions, Indiastack APIs - UPI and Aadhaar are actually being used at a national scale\\n\\nAdding crypto will allow (potentially) billions of Indian users to access pools of crypto capital from around the world\\n\\nForeign holders of Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other crypto assets want to invest in the Indian economy, and using a simple API they’ll be able to invest as low as $0.1\\n\\nThis level of flexibility would mean investment, not just in infrastructure and corporations, but in people - using micro-tasks and remote work\\n\\nIndia already develops digital assets for the world, this model would democratize direct access to highly-skilled remote work\\n\\nIf the internet connected Indians to millions of sources of information, crypto could connect them to millions of sources of capital\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642497696,\"title\":\"Add crypto to Indiastack?\"},\"digest\":\"Lix7NlT1UnSrNwoKKrRc4qGzsmN38eW0PBcndV8S_-A\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF41DF18b77bec4e196Ecf0178820313F9Fca3562\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0egU7ASP7p-8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"wzfzLBnv7cv0zfVJaRZxJt3DOz0v15d8p9j9SCzst6wBOzwRLkIFgPPOyLfEGSYomeFrDeOcfp4vrc5Ax6Rj8Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xfca35987db28220465f949e8414d396e911f842c8caa46dbdad7fad0118798ab7d26b8f7967ca9be532786093ace73c092ed916e94d8da872148d1a00a92891c1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"9MDTNFKkmPt6C40sVJhdzb51qYUjH7pg1dj_3mO4pF8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7qf62ZqRAbEAYWPawgfq4oYkqHbt4oD0egU7ASP7p-8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Lix7NlT1UnSrNwoKKrRc4qGzsmN38eW0PBcndV8S_-A\"}"